</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:46
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35941' id='t-35941'>For example, how many of you still have
